    "attributes": {
        "action": "Children who are registered for home education to have mandatory welfare checks.",
        "additional_details": "Children who are home schooled are at risk of becoming hidden children, with the opportunity to identify risks to their welfare in their home environment severely diminished. \r\nA simple welfare check on a monthly or quarterly basis would be key to preventing these scenarios.\r\n",
        "background": "When a child is removed from the school roll and registered for home education, there is a loss of the safeguarding layer of that child that teachers and schools currently provide. Parents have no legal obligation to let education department visit the home and determine if a suitable environment.",
